title: Your Mommy Kills Animals (2007)
description:
Synopsis:
This documentary about animal activism from director Curt Johnson features interviews with Hollywood stars including Katharine Heigl, Moby, Jessica Biel, and more. The film examines recent accusations by the FBI that categorize animal-rights movement leaders as potential terrorists.

Rated: R
Runtime: 1 hr 46 mins
Theatrical Release: Jul 20, 2007 Limited
Director: Curt Johnson
